contains several bugs that may seem easy to fix.  The reason why this
version is rushed, is that I am going away for the summer and at my
summerhouse I do not have the ability to communicate or use Internet.
If I had not released this version now, it would not have been made
available until mid-august...  I simply ran out of time before the
summer-holiday...  The bugs are however only minor ones, and I think you
can live with it...

If any questions, I will be available at my @{"summer-address" link Afterword}.

Have fun...
